    <item>
      <title>OSINT on a Budget: Recon Techniques That Actually Work</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/posts/osint-recon-techniques/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/posts/osint-recon-techniques/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;why-osint-matters-before-you-touch-a-single-port&#34;&gt;Why OSINT Matters Before You Touch a Single Port&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Reconnaissance is the phase most people rush. That&amp;rsquo;s a mistake.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The more you know before sending a single packet, the quieter your footprint — and the better your attack surface map.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;passive-recon-stack&#34;&gt;Passive Recon Stack&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;These are the tools I run on every engagement before active scanning:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# Certificate transparency — free, no auth needed&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;curl &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f1fa8c&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;https://crt.sh/?q=%25.target.com&amp;amp;output=json&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; | jq &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f1fa8c&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;.[].name_value&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; | sort -u&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# Wayback Machine URLs&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;waybackurls target.com | grep &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f1fa8c&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;\.php\|\.asp\|admin\|login&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# GitHub dorking&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;gh search code &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f1fa8c&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;target.com&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; --language&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;python&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;subdomain-enumeration&#34;&gt;Subdomain Enumeration&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Passive first, then active:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
